<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_d6c1f4e8-4c07-49cd-946f-912ad6bbd6a0" outputclass="ncc-clause"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>D3D25</sptc><title id="_55caf9bf-b8ac-47cc-960d-7b8c3ac81816">Swinging doors</title><archive-num>2019: D2.20</archive-num><subclause id="_b9763387-5b73-48c5-8850-a36ea6d16522" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_88b37e74-5413-4a51-b04a-e09945cfc4bc">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>A swinging door in a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_8a4d64d4-5891-43f9-af67-31bd19c675ce" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_cabbd9aa-5e90-4dad-82a6-8927056f9c91" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref> or forming part of a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_d6117cb0-3c6c-4d88-a9a9-5f26db22d206" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_44bbf72a-12ae-4698-ab46-b1299f69b51f" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref>—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_6c3d9da0-f092-45ee-a0d4-43ac5e14015c">must not encroach—<ol><li>at any part of its swing by more than 500 mm on the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_4675f7a8-6558-4f69-a7a5-72f7c1ad1464" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> width (including any landings) of a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_8afdcb45-7c54-492a-b6d3-5251f8d9cbf8" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> stairway, ramp or passageway if it is likely to impede the path of travel of the people already using the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_6f065b04-b259-4b73-bd1f-8ce1607a1cd1" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref>; and</li><li>when fully open, by more than 100 mm on the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_4b892f9d-460b-4834-914e-3e8050cd83de" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> width of the <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_a9ad4ea6-7655-4fbb-b626-07f67b26c199" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_c764dc15-194d-4ff0-b80e-04dc004453b8" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref>; and</li></ol></li><li id="_3c31eb39-ce3a-4bd9-b4f5-4087b033aa77">must swing in the direction of egress unless—<ol><li>it serves a building or part with a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1314_2.10.0.xml#_7da927fe-453e-424f-b6ec-280f4e464397" id="_589d1430-c7ac-4f72-b2cd-851d4091b850" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">floor area</xref> not more than 200 m<sup xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" id="_4ae9b30a-f91b-47b6-a02e-8829026b226e" inv:access="external">2</sup>, it is the only <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1432_4.0.0.xml#_af6fde9f-147d-4782-8b85-42044e80fd42" id="_e128eb6e-52d7-41c5-bc0f-2eef52543501" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">required</xref> <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_46f1b0ed-864b-4028-ab54-58af2ac08884" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">exit</xref> from the building or part and it is fitted with a device for holding it in the open position; or</li><li>it serves a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1445_0.13.0.xml#_b30a308f-eb9f-4549-a6c1-19d5f32a5272" id="_cfd2503a-1f1b-486b-9b76-3f3969326438" inv:access="external" scope="local" type="abcb-glossentry">sanitary compartment</xref> or airlock (in which case it may swing in either direction); and</li></ol></li><li id="_7bb54974-8a5a-4375-a8a2-1eaa1d4e0982">must not otherwise impede the path or direction of egress.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_28b1f5a8-d04d-4deb-959a-377b9526b889" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_8f8f02f8-c816-4eed-aaa1-2536949f45b3">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The measurement of encroachment referred to in (1)(a) in each case is to include door handles or other furniture or attachments to the door.</p></subclause></clause>